435
00:39:08,349 --> 00:39:11,988
This was only a small change, but I should still contribute.

436
00:39:15,358 --> 00:39:18,289
Besides, it's something I'm the best at.

437
00:39:20,429 --> 00:39:23,628
Unlike those haters online who fight on their computer keyboard,

438
00:39:23,628 --> 00:39:26,329
