527
00:45:05,669 --> 00:45:06,709
All right, then.

528
00:45:06,709 --> 00:45:09,279
We don't have much time, anyway. Let's speed this up.

529
00:45:09,709 --> 00:45:11,979
I know that you're going through a lot,

530
00:45:12,049 --> 00:45:14,250
